

Sudoku solver for X * X Sudoku

***************************************************************************

Naming convention:
one cell is referenced by c_1_1_vx

the first number is the column
the second number is the row
v = value
x is the value

Sudoku_Player:
This is the main class where the Sudoku is played.


Sudoku_Rule_Creator:
Takes an input value and creates the rules for the Sudoku in logical form.


CNF_File_Creator:
To pass it to the solver it is neccesarry to write the rules into a CNF Dimacs file. This class creates one.





